[{"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-24T21:00:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/96246b154ef58fd18277d8b741bd8fd8.jpg\"/><p>Amazon\u2019s live-action adaptation of Sega\u2019s hit <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/tag/yakuza\">Like a Dragon series</a> has finally landed, and the show is already making waves. Titled Like a Dragon: Yakuza, the gritty crime drama follows the series\u2019 longtime protagonist Kazuma Kiryu across two timelines: one as a teenage orphan in 1995, and the other as a hardened\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/like-a-dragon-yakuza-amazon-tv-show-reviews-roundup-1851680774\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 1383207, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/like-a-dragon-yakuza-amazon-tv-show-reviews-roundup-1851680774", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 175, "source_url": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/96246b154ef58fd18277d8b741bd8fd8.jpg", "title": "Amazon\u2019s Like A Dragon: Yakuza Is Already A Divisive Adaptation Of The Beloved Games", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-24T20:20:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/90c70f07a72cf849b74260ad1adf145d.jpg\"/><p><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/balatro-poker-roguelike-worth-it-is-it-good-review-pc-1851283124\">Balatro is a very, very good game</a>. We\u2019ve established that a few times here at Kotaku. And now, for all you folks still playing the roguelike poker game, a new update has added some fresh crossover cards featuring characters from Stardew Vally, Cyberpunk 2077, and Slay The Spire. </p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/balatro-crossover-friends-of-jimbo-cyberpunk-stardew-1851680749\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 1383208, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/balatro-crossover-friends-of-jimbo-cyberpunk-stardew-1851680749", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 175, "source_url": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/90c70f07a72cf849b74260ad1adf145d.jpg", "title": "One Of 2024's Best Games Continues Its Crossover Domination With Cyberpunk And Stardew Valley", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-24T19:55:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/fa2a45197d10860d3a32eb7a12ebec49.png\"/><p>The third big update for <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/star-wars-outlaws-review-size-how-big-hours-xbox-ps5-pc-1851631123\">Star Wars Outlaws </a>is finally here with promised improvements to stealth, NPC AI, and more. Unfortunately, the patch has also messed up how the game looks on PlayStation 5, with players reporting screen tearing issues that break the immersion of its normally gorgeous-looking open worlds. </p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/star-wars-outlaws-title-update-1-3-stealth-ps5-screen-1851680729\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 1383209, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/star-wars-outlaws-title-update-1-3-stealth-ps5-screen-1851680729", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 175, "source_url": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/fa2a45197d10860d3a32eb7a12ebec49.png", "title": "Star Wars Outlaws' New Patch Makes The Game Look Bad On PS5", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-24T19:48:21+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/6e5ef5c2ea9249107cf7a718649b1399.jpg\"/><p>Overwatch 2 announced it was considering <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/overwatch-2-5v5-6v6-team-comp-steam-juno-patch-1851605293\">testing out a return to its original 6v6 format</a> after swapping to its current, controversial 5v5 structure back when the sequel launched in 2022. Now, it sounds like that test is coming up sooner than originally expected, as Blizzard has announced it will bring back the format\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/overwatch-2-6v6-test-season-14-open-role-queue-date-1851680742\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 1382850, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/overwatch-2-6v6-test-season-14-open-role-queue-date-1851680742", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 175, "source_url": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/6e5ef5c2ea9249107cf7a718649b1399.jpg", "title": "Overwatch 2 Is Bringing Back 6v6 Sooner Than Expected", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-24T19:15:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/65d8eb42bb4ebac94613daf7948c4393.png\"/><p>The first patch for Dragon Ball: Sparking Zero is out and <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/dragon-ball-sparking-zero-yajirobe-senzu-bean-tier-op-1851669930\">it has demolished Yajirobe players</a> even more ruthlessly than that Saibaman wasted Yamcha. There is no coming back from this nerf, bean daddies. But at least the game runs better now due to some menu improvements and other bug fixes, even if a corrupted save\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/dragon-ball-sparking-zero-patch-notes-yajirobe-save-bug-1851680683\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 1382851, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/dragon-ball-sparking-zero-patch-notes-yajirobe-save-bug-1851680683", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 175, "source_url": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/65d8eb42bb4ebac94613daf7948c4393.png", "title": "Dragon Ball: Sparking Zero's First Update Is Live, Bringing Bean Daddies Everywhere To Their Knees", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-24T18:15:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/10deb3d09c0219f40004f0f491574949.jpg\"/><p>Over the last few years, <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/oh-god-fortnite-made-peely-worse-1844547798\">Peely</a>, a <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/even-apple-knows-fortnites-peely-is-a-monster-1846860238\">disturbing anthropomorphized banana</a>, has become Fortnite\u2019s de facto mascot. We here at Kotaku don\u2019t like that. This creepy bastard keeps coming back, even after death. So we are all happy to learn that Fortnite has finally skinned and flayed Peely. The bastard deserved it. </p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/fortnite-peely-leatherface-skins-halloween-leaks-1851680623\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 1382453, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/fortnite-peely-leatherface-skins-halloween-leaks-1851680623", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 175, "source_url": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/10deb3d09c0219f40004f0f491574949.jpg", "title": "Fortnite Flays Peely, World Cheers", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-24T17:45:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/7d5a8bab4b607c2e61a53964357e065e.jpg\"/><p>New York Comic Con is always a wild weekend in the city that never sleeps, and NYCC 2024 was no exception. Announcements are made over the subway speakers, directing out-of-town attendees towards the right trains to take them to the Jacob Javits Convention Center, and the streets are filled with cosplayers in various\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/nycc-cosplay-costume-best-new-york-comic-con-2024-1851680217\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 1382454, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/nycc-cosplay-costume-best-new-york-comic-con-2024-1851680217", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 175, "source_url": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/7d5a8bab4b607c2e61a53964357e065e.jpg", "title": "Here's Our Favorite Cosplay From NYCC 2024", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-24T17:35:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/f2b3f2af68ea9d55c2768542dcab50cf.jpg\"/><p>Destiny 2 players are convinced the game is secretly ripping them off. While on its face an epic space opera about humanity confronting cosmic evil in a post-apocalyptic future, Bungie\u2019s sci-fi  shooter is also a Pok\u00e9mon-style collectathon where instead of cute magical creatures, players capture rare, ornate, and\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/a-destiny-2-conspiracy-theory-gets-to-the-heart-of-its-1851680514\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 1382455, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/a-destiny-2-conspiracy-theory-gets-to-the-heart-of-its-1851680514", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 175, "source_url": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/f2b3f2af68ea9d55c2768542dcab50cf.jpg", "title": "A Destiny 2 Conspiracy Theory Gets To The Heart Of Its Biggest Loot Problem", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-24T17:10:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/21303c3b5ce1bdde51fb7e74122d1a5b.jpg\"/><p>There\u2019s no need to fret if you\u2019re yet to make solid Halloween plans. If you don\u2019t have a party or costume lined up, you can still find a theater doing a screening on the night, or if you\u2019re more inclined to stay indoors, maybe it\u2019s worth perusing sales for great horror games. Xbox is hosting a sale right now for\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/resident-evil-dead-space-alien-horror-xbox-sale-1851680538\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 1381963, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/resident-evil-dead-space-alien-horror-xbox-sale-1851680538", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 175, "source_url": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/21303c3b5ce1bdde51fb7e74122d1a5b.jpg", "title": "Eight Terrifying Games And Series To Pick Up During Xbox\u2019s Halloween Sale", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-24T17:00:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/314a3879d3c428f07e7b332fcf8ea890.jpg\"/><p>When I play a smaller game that really has an effect on me, I\u2019m usually cool with not getting more of it. The advantage of artful, smaller-scope projects is that they can concisely say what they need to say without being beholden to all the forever-game nonsense that infects the AAA space. However, I\u2019ll make an\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/slay-the-princess-pristine-cut-review-update-new-routes-1851678749\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 1381964, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/slay-the-princess-pristine-cut-review-update-new-routes-1851678749", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 175, "source_url": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/314a3879d3c428f07e7b332fcf8ea890.jpg", "title": "2023\u2019s Best Narrative Game Just Got Even Better", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-24T16:50:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/e9c15c4857f723762810dc78870a28fd.jpg\"/><p>The <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/john-wick-under-the-high-table-tv-keanu-reeves-1851614078\">John Wick series</a> is one of the biggest action movie franchises in the world right now, with multiple sequels, a TV series, and <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/john-wick-5-ballerina-trailer-ana-armas-keanu-reeves-1851658683\">a new film spin-off coming soon</a>. However, all of this might not have happened if it hadn\u2019t been for Desperate Housewives star Eva Longoria and a last-minute investment of $6 million. </p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/john-wick-eva-longoria-investment-last-minute-24-hours-1851680461\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 1381965, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/john-wick-eva-longoria-investment-last-minute-24-hours-1851680461", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 175, "source_url": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/e9c15c4857f723762810dc78870a28fd.jpg", "title": "John Wick Ran Out Of Money 24 Hours Before Filming, Then Eva Longoria Invested $6 Million", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-24T15:25:00+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/4880235b98f99738368b71af6241ab9e.jpg\"/><p>There\u2019s been a massive breakthrough in the world of Final Fantasy VII. Not the new remakes on PlayStation 5, but the original 1997 game. A new skip makes it possible to jump right to Aerith\u2019s death, earlier than players had ever expected. She\u2019ll still die in the pivotal scene, but players can keep her in the party\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/final-fantasy-vii-aerith-cheat-speedrun-sephiroth-ff7-1851680275\">Read more...</a></p>", "id": 1381563, "language": "en", "link": "https://kotaku.com/final-fantasy-vii-aerith-cheat-speedrun-sephiroth-ff7-1851680275", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 32, "page_rating_contents": 100, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 175, "source_url": "https://kotaku.com/rss", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/4880235b98f99738368b71af6241ab9e.jpg", "title": "Final Fantasy VII's Biggest Skip Ever Lets You 'Save' Aerith Without Cheats", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-24T15:12:45+00:00", "description": "<img class=\"type:primaryImage\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_80,w_636/c7b93cacd7479151648095f75682becb.jpg\"/><p>Earlier this month, Pok\u00e9mon developer Game Freak <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/pokemon-hack-teraleak-gen-10-switch-2-game-freak-beta-1851671688\">suffered a massive data breach</a> and ever since, details about and assets for projects new and old have been trickling out onto the internet. These have ranged from <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/pokemon-ruby-sapphire-water-starter-leak-rabbit-1851673279\">unused Pok\u00e9mon who never saw the light of day</a>, to <a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 lcFFec js_link\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/pokemon-game-freak-leaks-legends-z-a-gen-10-anime-movie-1851674254\">information on upcoming games</a> like next year\u2019s Pok\u00e9mon\u2026</p><p><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/pokemon-x-y-mega-jynx-evolution-form-leak-game-freak-185", "id": 1381090, "language": "en", "link": "https:/